        <Parent_String>chapels by function [300449013], chapels (rooms or structures) [300004590], Christian religious building spaces [300004560], religious building spaces [300004559], rooms and spaces by building type [300100051], rooms and spaces [300133704], built work divisions [300072553], components by specific context [300241584], components (objects parts) [300241583], Components (hierarchy name) [300241490], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
